# This file ensures the thumbnails directory is tracked by git
# Place manually processed thumbnail images here to override default Cloudflare images
# Supported formats: .jpg, .jpeg, .png, .webp, .gif
#
# Enhanced naming convention with fallback hierarchy (most specific first):
# 1. {contentId}-{orientation}-{containerSlug}-{variantSlug}-{languageId}.{ext}
# 2. {contentId}-{orientation}-{containerSlug}-{variantSlug}.{ext}
# 3. {contentId}-{orientation}-{containerSlug}.{ext}
# 4. {contentId}-{orientation}.{ext}
# 5. {contentId}.{ext}
#
# Examples:
# - 1_jf-0-0-vertical-watch-jesus-film-english-529.jpg (most specific)
# - 1_jf-0-0-vertical-watch-jesus-film-english.jpg
# - 1_jf-0-0-vertical-watch.jpg
# - 1_jf-0-0-vertical.jpg
# - 1_jf-0-0.jpg (fallback to basic contentId)
